                "invention-title": [
                    "Biomass cascade pyrolysis-microwave gasification hydrocarbon co-production integrated device and method",
                    "生物质梯级热解-微波气化碳氢联产一体化装置与方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a biomass cascade pyrolysis-microwave gasification hydrocarbon co-production integrated device and method. The device comprises an integrated reaction system, an internal and external radial energy supply system and a product separation and collection system which cooperate with one another. The method comprises the following steps: performing low-temperature pyrolysis on a raw material to greatly improve the wave absorbing characteristic, then performing microwave gasification and online reforming to prepare hydrogen-rich gas and co-produce a porous carbon product, combusting pyrolysis gas to supply heat for raw material drying and low-temperature pyrolysis reaction, separating and purifying the hydrogen-rich gas to prepare a high-purity hydrogen product, and returning separated gas as a gasifying agent to provide gasification reaction. The multi-system collaborative integrated design is adopted, the microwave product quality and the reaction efficiency are improved through low-temperature preheating, meanwhile, the high-grade electric energy consumption is greatly reduced, and self-produced low-grade heat energy is recycled for self-heating. The device is continuous and reliable in operation, compact, efficient, small in occupied area and high in overall economical efficiency, and the problems that biomass pyrolysis gasification hydrogen production technical equipment is huge, high in cost, difficult to popularize and the like are solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种生物质梯级热解‑微波气化碳氢联产一体化装置与方法，所述装置包括协同配合的一体化反应系统，内外径向供能系统，产物分离收集系统。该方法包括对原料首先低温热解大幅提高吸波特性，然后微波气化和在线重整制备富氢气体联产多孔碳产品，热解气体燃烧为原料干燥和低温热解反应供热，富氢气体分离提纯制备高纯氢气产品，分离气作为气化剂返回提供气化反应。本发明采用多系统协同集成一体化设计，低温预热解提升微波产品品质和反应效率，同时大幅降低高品位电能消耗，自产低品位热能循环回收自供热。本发明装置运行连续可靠，紧凑高效，占地体积小，整体经济性高，解决生物质热解气化制氢技术设备庞大、成本高、推广难等问题。"
                }
            ]
